{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>给定一个完全由数字字符（‘0’,‘1’,‘2’,…,‘9’）构成的字符串str，请写出str的p型编码串。例如：字符串122344111可被描述为\"1个1、2个2、1个3、2个4、3个1\"，因此我们说122344111的p型编码串为1122132431；类似的道理，编码串101可以用来描述1111111111；00000000000可描述为\"11个0\"，因此它的p型编码串即为110；100200300可描述为\"1个1、2个 0、1个2、2个0、1个3、2个0\"，因此它的p型编码串为112012201320。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"字符串p型编码 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出该字符串对应的p型编码串。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入仅一行，包含字符串str。每一行字符串最多包含1000个数字字符。<p>","examples":"<input>122344111\n</input><output>1122132431\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1145","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}